ode>universe</code> is one of the basic repositories maintained by ubuntu, =
but it's not enabled on live sessions by default.</p><p>To fix that, before=
 doing step 1, you need to enter this command in the terminal:</p><p><code>=
sudo add-apt-repository universe</code></p><p>Then you can proceed with the=
 rest of the guide with no problems.</p></div></div><span class=3D"post-med=
